#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_starlight.md:20
msgid "Compatibility"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_starlight.md:23
msgid ""
"This controller is a class compliant USB {term}`MIDI` and audio device, so "
"it can be used without any special drivers on GNU/Linux, macOS, and Windows."
" However, if you wish to use the ASIO sound {term}`API` under Windows, "
"please install the latest driver package available from the [Support "
"page](https://support.hercules.com/en/product/djcontrolstarlight-en/)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_starlight.md:26
msgid "Sound card setup"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_starlight.md:29
msgid ""
"This controller has built-in 4 channel output sound card, with main and "
"headphone output (both 3.5mm jack)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_starlight.md:31
msgid "Open **Preferences > Sound Hardware**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_starlight.md:32
msgid "Select the **Output** tab"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_starlight.md:33
msgid ""
"From the **Main** drop-down menu, select the audio interface, then "
"**Channels 1-2**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_starlight.md:34
msgid ""
"From the **Headphones** drop-down menu, select the audio interface, then "
"**Channels 3-4**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_starlight.md:35
msgid "Click **Apply** to save the changes."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_starlight.md:38
msgid ""
"More details about audio configuration can be found in the {ref}`here "
"<setup-laptop-and-external-card>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_starlight.md:41
msgid ""
"The **Main** and **Headphone** knobs are hardware controls and interact "
"directly with the integrated sound card’s output. Although they also send "
"{term}`MIDI` messages, they have NOT been mapped in Mixxx, so do not expect "
"an on-screen reaction when using them. This was done to prevent the knobs to"
" adjust both the gain on the controller’s sound card and in Mixxx."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_starlight.md:45
msgid ""
"The {ref}`gain staging section of this manual <djing-gain-staging>` explains"
" how to set your levels properly when using Mixxx."
msgstr ""

